CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 15, 1958, pg. A5, reads: "SORIEE DANCE DOLLIES - The glamorous presentation by six lovely lassies from Howe Studios added the glitter of the 'Follies' to the Business and Professional Women's international soiree, which was held at the Centre Ave. YMCA recently. in center is Wyetta Turner.  The others are, left to right: Andrea Dukes, Toni Lewis, Louise Lowery, Elizabeth Lowery and Hope Tucker. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Girls from Howe Studios in can-can dance costumes, including Wyetta Turner in center, and Andrea Dukes, Toni Lewis, Louise Lowery, Elizabeth Lowery, and Hope Tucker, posing with lifted skirts at Business and Professional Women's international soiree, in Centre Avenue YMCA
